'''赫氏海豚'''（學名：''Cephalorhynchus heavisidii''），又名'''海氏矮海豚'''，是[[黑白海豚属|黑白海豚属]]下的一種海豚，生活在[[納米比亞|納米比亞]]到[[南非|南非]]西海岸沿海地區。

==命名==

19世紀早期，有人在[[好望角|好望角]]附近捉到了一只海豚，這只海豚由[[英屬東印度公司|英屬東印度公司]]的赫维赛德船長（Captain Haviside）帶到英國，動物學家[[约翰·爱德华·格雷|约翰·爱德华·格雷]]在《Spicilegia Zoologica》一書中對其進行了描述。但是他把這名船長的名字“Haviside”和另外一個收集動物標本的外科醫生“Heaviside”弄混了，結果現在英語文學中赫氏海豚通常都叫做“Heaviside's Dolphin”。不過實際也有別的一些機構使用正確的原名。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Platt|first1=John R.|title=First Major Genetic Study of Elusive South African Dolphin Reveals a Species in Peril|url=http://blogs.scientificamerican.com/extinction-countdown/first-major-genetic-study-of-elusive-south-african-dolphin-reveals-a-species-in-peril/|website=Scientific American|accessdate=10 December 2015|archive-date=2015-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151211091726/http://blogs.scientificamerican.com/extinction-countdown/first-major-genetic-study-of-elusive-south-african-dolphin-reveals-a-species-in-peril/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Gray|first1=John Edward|title=Spicilegia Zoologica, , or original figures and short systematic descriptions of new and unfigured animals Pt 1|publisher=Treuttel, Würtz & Co.|location=London|page=2|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=L-dAAAAAcAAJ&pg=PA2|accessdate=10 December 2015|archive-date=2016-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603161214/https://books.google.com/books?id=L-dAAAAAcAAJ&pg=PA2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=x-iptRSGHIQC&pg=PA17|title=Whales, Dolphins, and Porpoises|first1=Kenneth Stafford|last1=Norris|accessdate=10 December 2015|archive-date=2016-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160521082920/https://books.google.com/books?id=x-iptRSGHIQC&pg=PA17|dead-url=no}}</ref>

